 CRandomNumberGeneratorRandom number generation (wrapper for boost). An instance of this class cannot be used by multiple threads at once (member functions are not const). However, the constructor is thread safe and different instances can be used safely in any number of threads. It is also guaranteed that all created instances will have a "random" random seed
